1. Reference: 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pXJb6ehTV0o&list=PLP6tw4Zpj-RJP2-YrhtkWqObMQ-AA4TDy&index=10

- https://vitejs.dev/guide/

2. Khoi tao vite project:
- dung npm:
    npm create vite@latest
- dung yarn: (nen dung yarn vi khoi tao server nhanh hon)
    yarn create vite
    chon javascript + swc
3. Start server:
- cd vao thu muc project vua tao
- chay yarn install de cai cac package can thiet
- sau do chay yarn dev
    + co the chay yarn dev --host de tao ra cac network. TH co nhieu may cung chung mang thi co the dung link network de vao
    VD: dung mobile vao link Network: http://192.168.56.1:5173/ de test responsive luon
    + TH thuong xuyen muon chay yarn dev --host thi co the add them --host vao trong script 
    "dev": "vite" trong file package.json. 
    "scripts": {
        "dev": "vite --host",
        ---
    },

4. Note for scripts trong package json:
    - "build": "vite build": dung de build code de day len production. 
        + khac voi react, code build se duoc dat trong thu muc dist
        + Trong mot so TH de thu muc qua sau (nhieu lop) => gay loi ko tim duoc file trong assets =>
        them --base=./ vao sau vite build de fix
        "scripts": {
            "build": "vite build --base=./",
            ---
        },
        Khi do no se tu them ./ vao truoc cac file trong index.html
        VD: 
        <script type="module" crossorigin src="/assets/index-BPgokE0a.js"></script>
        Sau khi them: 
        <script type="module" crossorigin src="./assets/index-BPgokE0a.js"></script>

    - "preview": "vite preview": 
        Sau khi chay lenh yarn build, source code se duoc build va dat trong thu muc dist.
        Chay preview thi no se chay code trong thu muc dist de test code truoc khi deploy len production. 
        Neu chua co thu muc dist thi se bao loi.

    - "lint": "eslint . --ext js,jsx --report-unused-disable-directives --max-warnings 0",

5. 